---
---

<header class="equipos-hero">
  <p class="eyebrow">LAS 48 SELECCIONES · MUNDIAL 2026</p>
  <h1>
    <span class="title-main">Álbum de</span>
    <span class="title-accent">Selecciones</span>
  </h1>
  <p class="subtitle">
    Explora, conoce y colecciona las 48 selecciones clasificadas al Mundial 2026.
    Cada ficha incluye datos clave, estilo de juego y fortalezas del rival.
  </p>
  <span class="fifa-badge" aria-label="48 selecciones · Mundial 2026">
    <img
      src="/assets/brand/fifa/fifa-world-cup-2026-lockup-dark.webp"
      alt=""
      aria-hidden="true"
      width="160"
      height="160"
      loading="lazy"
      decoding="async"
    />
    <span>48 selecciones · Mundial 2026</span>
  </span>
  <span class="decorative-star" aria-hidden="true">★</span>
</header>

<style>
  .equipos-hero {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    text-align: left;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.85rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 241, 214, 0.96), rgba(255, 228, 232, 0.9));
    color: var(--pm-orange-600);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 850;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.3em;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 3.4rem);
    font-weight: 950;
    line-height: 0.9;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18), 0 12px 24px rgba(6, 19, 38, 0.18);
  }

  .title-main {
    color: var(--pm-blue-900);
  }

  .title-accent {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pm-orange-500) 0%, var(--pm-red-500) 64%, var(--pm-yellow-600) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 12px rgba(255, 64, 88, 0.22));
  }

  .subtitle {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--pm-blue-900);
    font-size: clamp(0.78rem, 1vw, 0.88rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    max-width: 52ch;
  }

  .fifa-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    margin-top: 0.2rem;
    padding: 0.32rem 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(7, 23, 53, 0.12);
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
    color: var(--pm-blue-900);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .fifa-badge img {
    width: 1.7rem;
    height: 1.7rem;
    object-fit: contain;
    display: block;
  }

  .decorative-star {
    position: absolute;
    top: -0.4rem;
    right: -0.6rem;
    color: var(--pm-pink-500);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    opacity: 0.85;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(255, 47, 179, 0.5));
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .equipos-hero {
      gap: 0.4rem;
    }
    .decorative-star {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
